Package: gloBFPr
Type: Package
Title: Access Global Building Height Datasets
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Xiaohao",
      family = "Yang",
      email = "xiaohaoy111@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")
    ))
Description: Automated access and analysis of multidimensional building profile 
    in cities. The package provides tools to access, search, and download global 
    3D building footprint datasets (3D-GloBFP) generated by 
    Che et al. (2024) <doi:10.5194/essd-16-5357-2024>. 
    The package includes functions to download building height tiles, calculate 
    multidimensional building metrics, and analyze data.
